Just come find me later.

26
00:02:55,870 --> 00:02:58,360
- Hey, you bastard! 
- I will see you again.

27
00:02:58,360 --> 00:03:02,170
Hey!

28
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:42,810
Who are you?

29
00:04:47,990 --> 00:04:52,950
I've waited a long time to see you.

30
00:04:52,950 --> 00:04:54,480
Me?

31
00:04:54,480 --> 00:04:56,280
Yes!

32
00:04:56,280 --> 00:04:58,190
Teacher.

33
00:04:59,180 --> 00:05:02,570
A disciple I don't know about.

34
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:08,480
Then the person behind me is waiting for me too?

35
00:05:08,480 --> 00:05:10,120
What?

36
00:05:21,710 --> 00:05:24,930
I've waited a really long time...

37
00:05:24,930 --> 00:05:26,740
Sam Bong.

38
00:05:31,930 --> 00:05:33,210
You...

39
00:05:33,930 --> 00:05:35,670
You are...

40
00:05:37,260 --> 00:05:39,390
You came too.

41
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:42,810
You know me?

42
00:05:42,810 --> 00:05:44,600
Of course I do.

43
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:46,720
I know you very well.

44
00:05:46,720 --> 00:05:50,580
I don't know you. Who are you?

45
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:52,850
Then you? Who are you?

46
00:05:52,850 --> 00:05:55,430
